  "content": "\n \n \n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b994bc23-4b46-451b-7aa9-7bab07e95d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb2R91xJQdibib12DocfyvQSVy5wc74ozuSD2rGscuD0ibjmvCVT8l8G8O25MNa8oYGjz1jQYYtzia0umQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"505100688\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b994bc23-4b46-451b-7aa9-7bab07e95d00/public\"></span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：犀牛 英智</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">从海底的慢动作漂浮到战场的史诗旋转，这十个视频全是Google Veo 2的神来之笔！它能让你的点子秒变大片级画面，快来围观这场创意狂欢。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就在刚刚结束的Next 2025大会上，谷歌带来了一大堆产品的迭代升级，其中尤其受人瞩目的就要数Veo 2。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Veo 2为视频的创建、编辑和视觉效果添加了一套强大的功能集，使其从一个生成工具转变为一个全面的视频创作和编辑平台。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">例如，你可以移除视频中不需要的背景图像、徽标或干扰物，使它们在每一帧中都平滑完美地消失，看起来就像从未存在过一样。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b06b1e9f-78d8-43c0-0197-ab73d2e7ce00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.34285714285714286\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1050\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"198\" data-imgfileid=\"505100748\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b06b1e9f-78d8-43c0-0197-ab73d2e7ce00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">借助插值（Interpolation）功能，你可以定义视频序列的开始和结束，让Veo无缝生成连接帧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这确保了平滑过渡并保持视觉连续性，从而创造出精美且专业的最终成品。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fa08e03e-831d-4bca-b72e-d685582dd100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.34291010194624655\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"193\" data-imgfileid=\"505100694\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fa08e03e-831d-4bca-b72e-d685582dd100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Veo 2升级后，很快就出现了一大堆网友的实测视频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AIGC创作者MayorkingAl就在X上分享了几个惊艳的例子。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f91b386-d68a-474d-2f35-c756c964a800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38422818791946306\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1192\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1192\" data-height=\"458\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"216\" data-imgfileid=\"505100707\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f91b386-d68a-474d-2f35-c756c964a800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">来，一起敞开脑洞，想象这样一些场面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">跑车在山路上甩尾狂飙，轮胎冒出滚滚白烟，在夕阳光里燃爆全场。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c9925d73-57d9-4b38-cd40-791a7852e300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505100695\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c9925d73-57d9-4b38-cd40-791a7852e300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9ce36te1wao\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9ce36ty1nry\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">prompt：慢动作广角镜头，一辆跑车在山间弯道上漂移。轮胎冒出浓密的烟雾，滚滚而出，在温暖的夕阳光辉下，格外醒目</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一个满脸故事的侦探，在昏暗灯光下死盯线索，烟雾缭绕像老派黑白片。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3d7d005e-fb0b-4036-ee64-934048515d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505100696\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3d7d005e-fb0b-4036-ee64-934048515d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9ce3du8l1\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9ce3dup199x\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">prompt：特写镜头聚焦一位中年侦探，他眉头紧锁，眼神锐利，穿着一件皱巴巴的风衣。一盏台灯的低调照明下，轮廓分明，突显两鬓斑白的胡茬。他正仔细检查一件关键证据，烟雾在黑色电影风格的办公室中弥漫</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这可不是什么大片花絮，全是Google Veo 2的神级创作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它把你随手写的点子变成炸裂的视频，再配点Suno的热血配乐，简直是创意风暴。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">准备好了吗？一起冲进这场视觉狂欢！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">谷歌Veo 2视频创作</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌Veo 2就像个会拍电影的AI神器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随便扔个脑洞——比如海底慢动作漂浮，或者战场上360度旋转的史诗瞬间——它就能给你整出画面感爆棚的视频，每一帧都像在讲故事。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/142087fc-4487-4f74-c9c4-861a0f684c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505100697\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/142087fc-4487-4f74-c9c4-861a0f684c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9ce6g6r1tdb\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9ce6g7c1emu\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">prompt：跟拍镜头下，一名潜水员在珊瑚礁上方无重力般漂浮。气泡缓缓上升，阳光穿透海水，照亮了色彩斑斓的鱼群</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">还可以有360度的旋转镜头。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2ad364bc-5da6-4462-d212-153717e47100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505100698\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2ad364bc-5da6-4462-d212-153717e47100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9ce632hs5y\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9ce633524yp\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">prompt：360度旋转镜头围绕一名跪在战场中央的士兵，紧握着一件发光的神器。烟雾和火花纷飞，周围的混乱以超现实的慢动作旋转</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">光影、运镜、细节，全都能搞定，气氛拉满到让人起鸡皮疙瘩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">黄昏的城市里，摩托车手在车流中穿梭，尾灯和霓虹光影在头盔上跳跃。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就连头盔上的倒影都能有很好的处理。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c1326646-fd63-4b12-fcfb-4a5151240d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505100699\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c1326646-fd63-4b12-fcfb-4a5151240d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9ce72n3iwj\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9ce72nk23tk\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">prompt：黄昏时分，从摩托车骑手身后拍摄的过肩镜头，骑手在车流中穿梭。尾灯的光线闪过，霓虹灯光影在头盔上扭曲变幻，城市在急速后退中化作一片模糊</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">再一秒，镜头升起，夕阳下的金色田野波光粼粼，温柔得让人心动。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bce4467-1b08-414a-2d5a-1c232f576800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505100700\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bce4467-1b08-414a-2d5a-1c232f576800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9ce7dvpp52\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9ce7dw92407\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">prompt：升降镜头，起始于一名年轻女子仰卧在高草丛中，一片广袤的金色田野在风中泛起层层涟漪，夕阳在温暖的电影光线中落下</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">短发女子在飞驰的车里淡定涂着鲜红口红。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这画面不仅是真实，而且还有很强的电影感了。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7acc6dee-7165-4e5c-da94-10c4a9e49c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505100701\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7acc6dee-7165-4e5c-da94-10c4a9e49c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9ce7oouw8j\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9ce7opc1bxl\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">prompt：特写镜头中，一位留着利落黑色波波头的女士，在一辆行驶的汽车中涂抹艳丽的口红。街灯的光线划过车窗，光影在她专注的双眸上流转。昏暗的车厢内，光影晃动，她完成最后一笔涂抹</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">镜头切到暴雨战场，剑士斗篷狂甩，冲锋时身后雷电划破天际。这特效，好莱坞团队看了都得大呼真实。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/34e426fa-3a3b-4c71-64c0-6eda89239d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505100702\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/34e426fa-3a3b-4c71-64c0-6eda89239d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9ce7ykxala\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9ce7ylg24gf\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">prompt：侧面跟拍镜头，随着一名剑士在被雨水浸湿的战场上冲锋，他的斗篷随风狂舞，身后的闪电划破天际。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">再一眨眼，像坐上狂奔的列车，火车轰鸣而来。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9ce8ah813u3\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/35fbff67-5bd0-4b74-ce1b-d1b2022c0a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505100703\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/35fbff67-5bd0-4b74-ce1b-d1b2022c0a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);font-size: 13px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9ce8ah81ten\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">prompt：第一人称视角镜头，一列火车从后方疾驰而来，飞速穿过隧道，灯光闪烁，碎片飞舞，镜头紧紧跟随飞奔的车辆</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些画面都像是电影片段，全靠Google Veo 2把脑洞变现实！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">配合Freepik AI Suite的画面音效打磨，简直是创作者的终极外挂。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Freepik AI Suite</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Freepik AI Suite是个创意全能工具箱，专为设计师和内容创作者打造。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/38cd2ba6-2c95-402b-4683-77719feea900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5564320388349514\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1648\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"313\" data-imgfileid=\"505100705\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/38cd2ba6-2c95-402b-4683-77719feea900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它的AI图像生成器，能根据描述秒出高清大图，从写实到动漫风格随便挑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">支持Google Veo 2等多种模型，生成从电影感大片到活泼动画的各种风格，还能直接剪辑、加音效，效率拉满。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">编辑功能也很硬核：背景移除、图像放大、细节修饰，还能让角色在不同画面里保持一致。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://x.com/MayorKingAI/status/1909696314046402870</span></span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "评测谷歌 Veo 2 能够将文字 prompt 转化为电影级视觉效果的强大功能，并介绍了 Freepik AI Suite 创意工具箱，展示 AI 在视频创作领域的潜力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "评测谷歌 Veo 2 能够将文字 prompt 转化为电影级视觉效果的强大功能，并介绍了 Freepik AI Suite 创意工具箱，展示 AI 在视频创作领域的潜力。",
  "summary": "文章主要介绍了谷歌 Veo 2 的升级及其在视频创作方面的强大功能。Veo 2 通过简单的文字 prompt，能够生成高质量、电影级的视频片段，极大地降低了视频创作的门槛。文章通过多个示例展示了 Veo 2 在不同场景下的应用，如跑车漂移、侦探故事、海底世界和战场等，突出了其在光影、运镜和细节处理方面的优势。此外，文章还介绍了 Freepik AI Suite，这是一个与 Veo 2 配合使用的创意工具箱，可以进一步提升视频创作的效率和质量。整体而言，文章旨在展示 AI 技术在视频创作领域的巨大潜力，以及为视频创作者和 AI 爱好者带来的便利。",
